      • classifyToken

        public static ClassifiedToken classifyToken(Token token)
        Classify token, metamap style.

        What are the classes?: 

          "ws" - whitespace
  "an" - alphanumeric
  "pn" - punctuation
  "uc" - uppercase
  "ic" - ignore case
  "lc" - lowercase
  "nu" - numeric
  "gr" - greek
  "op" - open paren
  "cp" - close paren
  "ob" - open bracket
  "cb" - close bracket
  "cm" - comma
  "un" - unknown"
        Parameters:
        token - original unclassified tokenlist
        Returns:
        token with classified tokens
